@startuml Add-To-Cart
actor Customer
participant "Frontend" as F
participant "Backend API" as B
database "Supabase" as DB

Customer -> F: Click Add to Cart
F -> F: Update local cart state
F -> B: POST /cart (sync quantities)
note right: Session cookie included
B -> B: Get customerId from session
B -> DB: Upsert CartItem records
DB --> B: OK
B -> B: Get cart
B --> F: Updated cart items
F --> Customer: Show updated cart badge
@enduml
